  "body": "## What's Changed\r\n* feat: add CROC_PORT and CROC_PORTS env vars by @hangone in https://github.com/schollz/croc/pull/1099\r\n* Dockerfile: bump builder image to golang:1.25 by @c-tonneslan in https://github.com/schollz/croc/pull/1108\r\n* Honor `CROC_SECRET` for `send` secret selection on Linux/macOS by @Copilot in https://github.com/schollz/croc/pull/1110\r\n* chore: update dependencies by @schollz in https://github.com/schollz/croc/pull/1111\r\n* chore: bump v10.4.4 by @schollz in https://github.com/schollz/croc/pull/1112\r\n\r\n## New Contributors\r\n* @hangone made their first contribution in https://github.com/schollz/croc/pull/1099\r\n* @c-tonneslan made their first contribution in https://github.com/schollz/croc/pull/1108\r\n\r\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/schollz/croc/compare/v10.4.3...v10.4.4",
